## Features

Your MC knows how to drop the beats! ğŸµ

- ğŸ“¦ **Track Info** - Get the full story on any PyPI package (metadata, versions, dependencies)
- ğŸ **Compatibility Check** - Know which Python versions can handle your tracks
- ğŸ” **Deep Mixing** - Advanced dependency analysis and recursive resolution to avoid conflicts
- ğŸ“¥ **Collection Building** - Download packages with all their dependencies for offline mixing
- ğŸ“Š **Chart Analysis** - Real-time download statistics and popularity trends 
- ğŸ† **Top 40** - Discover the hottest packages trending right now
- ğŸ”’ **Security Scanning** - Keep your playlist safe from vulnerable packages
- ğŸ“„ **License Mixing** - Ensure your package mix is legally compatible
- ğŸ¥ **Health Check** - Assess package quality across 7 key metrics
- ğŸ“‹ **Setlist Analysis** - Parse and analyze requirements files in any format
- ğŸ¯ **Smart Prompts** - MCP templates for guided decision-making
- ğŸ¢ **Private Venues** - Support for private PyPI repositories  
- âš¡ **Live Performance** - Fast async operations with intelligent caching
- ğŸ› ï¸ **Universal Mixer** - Easy integration with all MCP clients

