## ğŸ›ï¸ Configuration

<div align="center">

**mcpypi works with ALL major MCP clients!**

[![Claude Desktop](https://img.shields.io/badge/Claude_Desktop-Ready-blue?style=for-the-badge&logo=anthropic)](https://claude.ai/desktop)
